Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:36.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,个子好高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 小哥打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有兴趣当发型模特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:45.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,免费？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:46.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只剪个头发的话没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个发型不热吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剪掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太想剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:02:59.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:02.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笃也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 找你好久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:06.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是般配的情侣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我还不太熟悉这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是路痴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不用特地来邻镇的暑期补习也行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为早苗在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神对上了 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头发还是那么长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗变得更加漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:47.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,时隔六年 在亲戚家的葬礼上与早苗再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她和班上的女生完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我基本没有兄弟和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我唯一一个表姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？桐{\fn方正中等线_GBK}嶋{\r}笃也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:04.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇 她正往这边看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好大只！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前不是才到我这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她还记得我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:25.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗也变得很成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我才没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好美 跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗她表现出一副极其厌恶的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回想结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗变得更加漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为女演员什么的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？不 我想成为大学生来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不断纠缠 不肯放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道早苗有了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:07.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说你在高中有了喜欢的人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然并不是因为这个就要怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那家伙好像相处的并不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着最近的你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是体贴入微的倾诉对象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,血脉相连的男性朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:36.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 早苗的任何事情我都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人 是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是无法喜欢上笃也你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:52.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗是因为她是女孩子所以才喜欢她的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她是女孩子所以才无法进展顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂复杂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可能有点粗神经
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:10.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是早苗第一次喜欢上某人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有些开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是早苗喜欢的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:17.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我大概是讨厌男生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是不讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是把桐{\fn方正中等线_GBK}嶋{\r}笃也当作一个人来看待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:39.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以与性别什么的无关么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:40.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:44.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想把笃也你贴上性别的标签
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是因为给那个人也贴上性别的标签所以才喜欢的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我的机会也不是零嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 眼神对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,学习？学了学了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们俩都很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:12.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是优等生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:25.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想听到对方的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我明白肯定不成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把我当成她也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这种情况特地说出来感觉更奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我和麦 本来就是以这为前提的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:51.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…只有我觉得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…什么什么 我不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:03.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快说啊 不说出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我想的是一样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉不知何时起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法把花火你当成替身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:20.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说 那个 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么…说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:27.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 那个 不快点说些什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我们彼此都做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能尽力达成目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我也清楚地意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:57.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无法再把麦当成哥哥的替身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里就好了 谢谢你送我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,时间无法倒流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H575E56&\b1\fs52.5\bord0\frz350.8\frx26\fry356\pos(1296,189)}在吗、在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H575E56&\b1\fs52.5\bord0\frz351.8\frx30\fry356\pos(978,405)}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:19.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开始戴眼镜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:25.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还合适吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很有老师的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你通过教师考试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:32.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:36.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的只是中考啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有 那也是个难关哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥实现了自己的梦想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:45.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很厉害 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 干嘛啦要哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:51.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到小花也长大了不自觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又把我当小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:05.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗？小花在雪天迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回家路上我们牵着手一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那么久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就今天 到家为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 很难为情的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发光的众多回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:28.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是些琐碎的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直珍藏到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:39.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你能记住这些回忆中的一项
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不带丝毫夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能凭此活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能比你更好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都找不到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H575E56&\b1\fs52.5\bord0\frz350.8\frx26\fry356\pos(1296,189)\blur15\alpha&HA9&\t(0,381,\blur0\alpha&H00&)}在吗、在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H575E56&\b1\fs52.5\bord0\frz351.8\frx30\fry356\pos(978,405)\blur15\alpha&HA9&\t(0,381,\blur0\alpha&H00&)}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H575E56&\b1\fs52.5\bord0\frz351.8\pos(1092,135)\frx36\fry356}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H575E56&\b1\fs49.5\bord0\fad(200,0)\frx352\fry352\frz352\pos(1044,501)}星期天能稍微见一面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算扭曲 就算笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都竭尽全力地爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H8F8139&\b1\fs52.5\bord0\pos(1032,456)}老师 这周周日能见一面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H9B9894&\b1\fs52.5\bord0\pos(648,837)}可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不会再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作业 做完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:37.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 麦是明天白天 我在晚上 去表白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是失恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:47.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这总比一个人好 两个人一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:54.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 明天22点 在这里见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:02.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得无法直视麦的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为何呢事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 脸好热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:21.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:30.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在鼓励我吗 麦那般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:35.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 心不慌手不抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会对麦心跳加速真的奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能否 有所进步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,梦到手牵手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:16.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麦 怎么了 真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:20.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 特意叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:24.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 这是为了我可爱的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小麦是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是进路的烦恼商谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:34.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始 我会被这个人甩掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既然不能摘掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:39.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,站着说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:48.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 呃 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:52.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师口渴了 不如去咖啡店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全被牵着鼻子走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麦晒黑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 骗人 真特么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前还在意真的晒不黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:15.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是在挖苦我么 长得白还不容易黑的 真让人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我这已经是超过了白色 更像没血色的苍白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像死掉似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:25.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我觉得女孩子更喜欢那样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 是喜欢偶像系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说喜欢麻利的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师喜欢漂亮的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 虽然也有和秃头大叔睡过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:44.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:47.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:50.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:01.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:14.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我对麦你是喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 别偷偷高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你满口胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:22.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我一直看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放手吧真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再陷进去了 我这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:36.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对不可能泡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:50.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:55.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你是绝对 对我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:17:00.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的这个人 在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说谎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直对麦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明决定了 我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让你一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事先说明 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:26.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 无可救药的水性杨花的性格恶劣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只爱自己的性格扭曲的渣女这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明无法喜欢上任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却是得不到别人的欢心就浑身难受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:38.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…我的好意 也并不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也可以 就算不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:48.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱 那为什么跟过来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:52.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 这是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:57.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是村民LV1挑战最终BOSS的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢什么的 绝对不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对的战力差距
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:06.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像单薄纸片一样的喜欢根本没有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:14.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 所以 我之所以在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为你的第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 改变你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 安乐冈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的作业 做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好久没见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 暑假是会见不到老师的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:48.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是什么重要的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是…什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:56.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:01.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥这点 我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 在玩我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢过你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:06.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,过去式？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:07.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:19.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,几时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在也迟钝得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:27.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,马上意识到了就会认真起来这点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:27.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:33.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很久…很久很久以前开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:37.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的心情能同步考虑这点我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:41.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一但说话 就会接连溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:44.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,声音喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相貌喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,举止喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说话方式喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑的样子喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的地方喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:57.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在最重要的时候 像这样接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:08.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个 知道的 这颤抖是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:12.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚地知道你喜欢的并不是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样哭着 是多久没试过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥这样紧紧地紧紧地抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:28.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我确切地感受到是第一次也是最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:29.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,继续在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:34.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全身一丝不剩地接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:38.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被他所珍视我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我这漫长的单恋也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:00.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才要向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不是一个人
